I stood apart, master of codes and lost worlds,

00:03:12.019 --> 00:03:17.510
of heat and cold and the sleep of a hundred
million years.

00:03:17.510 --> 00:03:27.069
A lost world is a sort of scientific myth,
an evolutionary scenario in which an ecosystem

00:03:27.069 --> 00:03:29.080
is
isolated and preserved.

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:34.030
The rest of the world changes, leaving a tiny,
fragile pocket where

00:03:34.030 --> 00:03:35.970
ancient species survive.

